The community was first listed as a [[census designated place]] under the name '''Basye-Bryce Mountain''' in the [[2000 U.S. census]];<ref name=2000CensusVA/> and renamed '''Basye''' for the [[2010 U.S. census]].<ref name=2010CensusVA/>

